774
01:03:29,539 --> 01:03:30,579
Honey...

775
01:03:31,579 --> 01:03:32,622
Cathy's here.

776
01:04:06,371 --> 01:04:07,662
What's his name?

777
01:04:20,839 --> 01:04:22,707
His name is...

778
01:04:22,791 --> 01:04:23,870
...Althan.

779
01:04:29,207 --> 01:04:30,370
Althan.

780
01:04:45,207 --> 01:04:50,291
Mr. Malik, your wife needs to keep using the
extracorporeal membrane oxygenation machine.

781
01:04:51,663 --> 01:04:55,663
Medically, she's still alive
with the help of the machine.

782
01:04:55,747 --> 01:05:00,914
But there's nothing else we can do
until she recovers from her coma.

783
01:05:46,631 --> 01:05:49,123
Be strong and be patient.

784
01:05:49,207 --> 01:05:52,999
I know you've done your best for Hannah.

785
01:05:53,079 --> 01:05:55,246
But if she's not out of this condition...

786
01:05:56,747 --> 01:05:57,914
...it'll be a pity for her.

787
01:06:18,663 --> 01:06:22,455
Oh dear. Sorry to keep you waiting this long.

788
01:06:22,539 --> 01:06:24,622
- It's okay.
- Let's go.

789
01:06:31,623 --> 01:06:32,954
What's wrong with you?

790
01:06:36,039 --> 01:06:37,291
What do you think?

791
01:06:38,707 --> 01:06:41,123
Are you asking me as your wife?

792
01:06:42,415 --> 01:06:43,622
Or as a doctor?

793
01:06:46,419 --> 01:06:48,003
Both.

794
01:06:48,087 --> 01:06:49,419
As a wife...

795
01:06:50,791 --> 01:06:54,747
...I will always support my husband's decision.

796
01:06:54,831 --> 01:06:57,999
But as a doctor...

797
01:06:59,955 --> 01:07:05,207
...medically, the only thing
that is keeping Hannah alive right now...

798
01:07:05,291 --> 01:07:07,574
...is the machine.

799
01:07:13,507 --> 01:07:14,587
Hey.

800
01:07:14,863 --> 01:07:15,958
Honey.

801
01:07:16,455 --> 01:07:17,914
It's okay.

802
01:07:33,499 --> 01:07:34,622
Hey.

803
01:07:38,539 --> 01:07:39,870
It's fine.

804
01:07:42,579 --> 01:07:44,703
You don't need to force everything.

805
01:07:46,371 --> 01:07:50,162
If you can't, don't do it.

806
01:07:53,207 --> 01:07:54,454
It's okay.

807
01:08:47,915 --> 01:08:51,830
Honey, I'm sorry if what I did is wrong.

808
01:08:52,999 --> 01:08:55,998
I'm sorry.

809
01:08:56,079 --> 01:08:59,078
I just don't want you to suffer any longer.

810
01:09:36,123 --> 01:09:39,455
I bear witness that there is no deity
(none truly to be worshipped) but Allah...

811
01:09:39,539 --> 01:09:42,791
...and I bear witness
that Muhammad is the messenger of Allah.

812
01:09:42,871 --> 01:09:45,079
I bear witness that there is no deity
(none truly to be worshipped) but Allah...

813
01:09:46,207 --> 01:09:49,206
...and I bear witness
that Muhammad is the messenger of Allah.

814
01:11:22,791 --> 01:11:23,998
Hannah?

815
01:11:27,539 --> 01:11:28,623
Honey?

816
01:11:30,831 --> 01:11:32,623
Thank God.

817
01:11:32,707 --> 01:11:35,291
God has shown His greatness.

818
01:11:35,371 --> 01:11:37,415
Nothing is impossible for Him.

819
01:11:38,331 --> 01:11:39,538
Come with me.

820
01:11:55,371 --> 01:11:56,371
Hannah?

821
01:11:57,287 --> 01:11:58,366
Na?

822
01:12:00,079 --> 01:12:01,455
Hannah?

823
01:12:01,539 --> 01:12:03,579
You're awake.

824
01:12:03,663 --> 01:12:05,539
Hi, honey.

825
01:12:05,623 --> 01:12:07,578
Thank God!

826
01:12:10,415 --> 01:12:12,247
Why am I here?

827
01:12:14,455 --> 01:12:16,579
Did you forget?

828
01:12:16,663 --> 01:12:18,291
But you remember me, don't you?

829
01:12:18,371 --> 01:12:19,370
Malik.

830
01:12:23,331 --> 01:12:24,619
Hi, Han.

831
01:12:24,871 --> 01:12:26,039
Who is this?

832
01:12:27,123 --> 01:12:29,331
Honey, this is Cathy.

833
01:12:29,415 --> 01:12:30,499
Cathy?

834
01:12:30,579 --> 01:12:32,663
- She was...
- I'm...

835
01:12:33,767 --> 01:12:34,890
...your doctor.

836
01:12:38,579 --> 01:12:45,079
Because you’ve just woken up from your long coma,
you need to rest a lot.

837
01:12:45,163 --> 01:12:46,578
Excuse me.

838
01:12:59,247 --> 01:13:00,291
Cathy.

839
01:13:03,183 --> 01:13:05,727
Why did you tell Hannah...

840
01:13:05,811 --> 01:13:07,914
...that you're her doctor?

841
01:13:08,000 --> 01:13:09,791
Well, I am.

842
01:13:09,871 --> 01:13:11,122
I mean...

843
01:13:12,579 --> 01:13:14,454
...I was going to say that...

844
01:13:16,291 --> 01:13:18,414
...that you're my wife.

845
01:13:22,831 --> 01:13:24,871
I talked to Dr. Mulia.

846
01:13:27,663 --> 01:13:28,915
He said that...

847
01:13:30,915 --> 01:13:33,707
...Hannah is having amnesia anterograde.

848
01:13:33,791 --> 01:13:37,955
She can't remember what has just happened.

849
01:13:38,039 --> 01:13:42,331
She can only remember information
or events that happened in the past.

850
01:13:42,415 --> 01:13:46,454
That's why she can't remember who I am.

851
01:13:49,623 --> 01:13:51,370
And why she forgot that...

852
01:13:53,579 --> 01:13:54,830
...we're married.

853
01:13:57,747 --> 01:14:00,707
I'll try to tell her.

854
01:14:00,791 --> 01:14:02,515
Malik, don't.

855
01:14:02,599 --> 01:14:04,367
For now...

856
01:14:05,371 --> 01:14:08,038
...don't burden her mind too much.

857
01:14:13,039 --> 01:14:14,747
Let's just wait...

858
01:14:14,831 --> 01:14:16,747
...until she fully recovers.

859
01:14:19,415 --> 01:14:20,579
What do you mean?

860
01:14:23,539 --> 01:14:24,915
I doubt...

861
01:14:26,291 --> 01:14:29,538
...that Hannah's decision to ask us to marry...

862
01:14:32,455 --> 01:14:34,830
Maybe she didn't fully realize it.

863
01:14:36,963 --> 01:14:38,579
I'm scared, Malik.

864
01:14:38,663 --> 01:14:42,163
I'm scared that when she remembers everything...

865
01:14:42,247 --> 01:14:44,955
...she can't accept that we're married.

866
01:14:46,207 --> 01:14:49,915
But everything has happened. You're my wife now.

867
01:14:50,000 --> 01:14:52,706
And I want you to still be there
for me and Althan.

868
01:15:22,831 --> 01:15:23,998
Hey.

869
01:15:24,079 --> 01:15:25,415
Nana, what are you doing?

870
01:15:25,499 --> 01:15:28,331
- I'm going to check on Althan.
- He's... Stop it.

871
01:15:28,415 --> 01:15:32,791
- You can't be tired. Don't move too much. Take rest.
- The baby's crying. That poor little thing.

872
01:15:32,871 --> 01:15:37,999
- I want to see him.
- Let him be, honey. Titi's there to take care of him.

873
01:15:38,079 --> 01:15:39,162
Titi's there already.

874
01:15:42,955 --> 01:15:45,039
Cathy is your doctor, honey.

875
01:15:45,123 --> 01:15:46,914
She was also our friend back in high school.

876
01:15:48,163 --> 01:15:50,498
While you were in a coma,
she took care of Althan.

877
01:15:55,415 --> 01:15:56,663
So all this time...

878
01:15:58,000 --> 01:15:59,291
...she has been living here?

879
01:15:59,371 --> 01:16:00,579
She has.

880
01:16:00,663 --> 01:16:03,370
Sometimes she needs to stay the night
because Althan can't be left alone.

881
01:16:08,039 --> 01:16:09,999
Don't think about it. Just rest.

882
01:16:10,079 --> 01:16:12,039
Why is she willing to do that?

883
01:16:14,207 --> 01:16:17,331
If you were in her position,
I'm sure you'd do the same thing.

884
01:16:19,623 --> 01:16:21,498
Because you have a big heart.

885
01:16:27,039 --> 01:16:28,623
Help me.

886
01:16:28,707 --> 01:16:31,579
- Your legs...
- They're so weak.

887
01:16:31,663 --> 01:16:32,791
Hi, Han.

888
01:16:34,331 --> 01:16:35,515
Hi.

889
01:16:35,579 --> 01:16:37,330
You still can't remember who I am?

890
01:16:42,187 --> 01:16:43,791
Han...

891
01:16:43,871 --> 01:16:45,915
...I'm Cathy.

892
01:16:46,000 --> 01:16:48,247
Your friend from high school.

893
01:16:48,331 --> 01:16:50,746
We often hung out together back in school.

894
01:16:53,291 --> 01:16:59,163
Hang on. I think I still kept our photo
from back then.

895
01:16:59,247 --> 01:17:02,798
Here. See? It was a long time ago.

896
01:17:07,663 --> 01:17:09,455
It's okay.

897
01:17:09,539 --> 01:17:14,038
Okay, I'm Cathy Meow.

898
01:17:16,755 --> 01:17:17,839
Meow.

899
01:17:19,923 --> 01:17:22,078
Cathy...

900
01:17:24,547 --> 01:17:27,135
Cathy Meow.

901
01:17:27,219 --> 01:17:30,079
Cathy... Cathy!

902
01:17:30,163 --> 01:17:31,998
Cathy! Oh God!

903
01:17:32,079 --> 01:17:33,747
Yes, I remember.

904
01:17:33,831 --> 01:17:36,851
So sorry. Oh dear!

905
01:17:38,039 --> 01:17:40,163
By the way, thanks a lot.

906
01:17:40,247 --> 01:17:41,579
Malik has told me.

907
01:17:42,579 --> 01:17:45,455
You took care of Althan while I was in a coma.

908
01:17:45,539 --> 01:17:46,662
Han...

909
01:17:48,207 --> 01:17:50,663
...I love Althan so much.

910
01:17:50,747 --> 01:17:52,539
And if you allow me...

911
01:17:53,431 --> 01:17:55,670
...I'd love to keep taking care of him.

912
01:17:58,455 --> 01:18:00,039
For sure.

913
01:18:01,791 --> 01:18:05,999
Hello, Mother. Your son is sleeping.

914
01:18:06,079 --> 01:18:10,123
- He was sleepy after his bath.
- Honey. Come here.

915
01:18:11,163 --> 01:18:12,955
Hello, Son.

916
01:18:13,039 --> 01:18:18,579
There are always lies in polygamy.

917
01:18:18,663 --> 01:18:21,747
Our boss asked us to lie, didn't he?

918
01:18:21,831 --> 01:18:25,247
Right. But it's for the good of everybody.

919
01:18:25,331 --> 01:18:27,663
Look at Mrs. Hannah, she's still unwell.

920
01:18:27,747 --> 01:18:31,207
They'll tell her slowly. Be patient.

921
01:18:31,291 --> 01:18:33,707
- You bad woman.
- Why are you hitting me?

922
01:18:33,791 --> 01:18:36,207
You're the doctor's supporter. Team Cheater.

923
01:18:36,291 --> 01:18:41,499
I'm not on anyone's team. I take no side.

924
01:18:41,579 --> 01:18:46,999
Let it go. Let's just pray that they get along well
and be happy. Just look at them.

925
01:18:47,079 --> 01:18:50,999
Hey. Cut your ear if they get along well.

926
01:18:51,079 --> 01:18:55,291
I've had experiences with being cheated on.

927
01:18:55,371 --> 01:18:58,539
It hurts so much here.

928
01:18:58,623 --> 01:19:02,663
Look. She can smile on the outside,
but I bet she wants to choke her.

929
01:19:02,747 --> 01:19:04,791
Don't choke me.

930
01:19:04,871 --> 01:19:08,039
Sorry, Bi Ipah.

931
01:19:08,123 --> 01:19:10,915
Don't think everyone is the same as you.

932
01:19:10,999 --> 01:19:13,415
Look at them.

933
01:19:13,499 --> 01:19:19,123
They're educated, smart, and able to think.
They have brains. Got it?

934
01:19:19,207 --> 01:19:23,831
You think I have nothing inside my skull?

935
01:19:23,915 --> 01:19:27,831
- It's not like that.
- You ugly Sundanese!

936
01:19:27,915 --> 01:19:30,663
What? Ugly Sundanese what?

937
01:19:30,747 --> 01:19:32,955
- What?
- Nothing.

938
01:19:33,039 --> 01:19:37,331
You'll think of me as a narcissist,
talking about an ethnic group.

939
01:19:37,415 --> 01:19:39,662
Not "narcist"...

940
01:19:42,079 --> 01:19:43,078
I'm tired.

941
01:19:44,831 --> 01:19:46,871
I'm also tired.

942
01:19:46,955 --> 01:19:47,998
Do you know?

943
01:19:49,295 --> 01:19:55,374
My biggest reason to stay alive is you.

944
01:19:56,579 --> 01:20:00,135
I want to stay with you forever.

945
01:20:00,219 --> 01:20:02,915
I want to be with you until I'm old.

946
01:20:02,999 --> 01:20:07,246
Okay, honey. We're going to grow old together.

947
01:20:30,663 --> 01:20:33,079
Honey...

948
01:20:33,163 --> 01:20:34,539
Hello, Son.

949
01:20:34,623 --> 01:20:35,882
Hi, honey.

950
01:20:36,999 --> 01:20:40,331
It's me, your mom.

951
01:20:40,415 --> 01:20:43,974
- What's wrong, kid? It's your mom.
- It's me, your mother.

952
01:20:45,751 --> 01:20:46,791
Cath...

953
01:20:46,875 --> 01:20:48,750
Honey, it's me, your mom.

954
01:20:53,391 --> 01:20:57,546
What's wrong? Oh, honey. It's okay, kid.

955
01:21:04,623 --> 01:21:05,707
It's okay.

956
01:21:05,791 --> 01:21:07,246
It's okay, kid.

957
01:21:10,123 --> 01:21:15,499
Cath, if you want to eat something
or if you crave anything...

958
01:21:15,579 --> 01:21:18,291
...just ask Mbok Ipah, okay?

959
01:21:18,371 --> 01:21:20,455
Okay, Han. Thank you.

960
01:21:20,539 --> 01:21:24,707
I promised Titi to cook her my fish recipe.

961
01:21:24,791 --> 01:21:26,538
It'll be so good.

962
01:21:28,000 --> 01:21:29,370
You call her Titi?

963
01:21:37,663 --> 01:21:39,123
I do.

964
01:21:39,207 --> 01:21:45,055
I usually call people by their last syllable.
Just like I call you Nana. Am I right?

965
01:21:45,123 --> 01:21:47,122
That's how I call my other friends, too.

966
01:21:48,343 --> 01:21:49,463
Do you forget?

967
01:21:50,163 --> 01:21:51,370
And what do you call him?

968
01:21:57,163 --> 01:21:58,871
I...

969
01:21:58,955 --> 01:22:00,707
...call him...

970
01:22:00,791 --> 01:22:01,831
...Malik.

971
01:22:03,455 --> 01:22:04,539
Malik, honey.

972
01:22:05,539 --> 01:22:07,138
I thought you call him "Liklik".

973
01:22:08,463 --> 01:22:10,319
So funny.

974
01:22:11,831 --> 01:22:13,206
"Liklik".

975
01:22:28,623 --> 01:22:31,706
Malik, I can't keep doing this.

976
01:22:33,291 --> 01:22:36,414
I’m feeling more guilty every day.

977
01:22:44,247 --> 01:22:46,118
It's time for us to be frank with her.

978
01:22:50,415 --> 01:22:54,163
But what if she can't accept everything?

979
01:22:54,247 --> 01:22:55,622
She'll accept it.

980
01:22:59,163 --> 01:23:01,415
We're going to find a good time to talk to her.

981
01:23:01,499 --> 01:23:02,662
Okay?

982
01:23:28,163 --> 01:23:30,246
I'm fine.

983
01:23:32,135 --> 01:23:34,371
- Morning, Mbok.
- Morning, Madame Doctor.

984
01:23:34,455 --> 01:23:36,415
- Morning, Han.
- Morning.

985
01:23:36,499 --> 01:23:38,499
- Morning, Ti.
- You don't need to. I'm fine.

986
01:23:38,579 --> 01:23:41,499
You look pretty today. Fresh.

987
01:23:41,579 --> 01:23:43,218
Did you sleep well last night?

988
01:23:44,623 --> 01:23:48,623
Yeah. It rained last night, so I slept better.

989
01:23:48,707 --> 01:23:49,915
Oh.

990
01:23:50,000 --> 01:23:51,746
It's okay. I can do it myself.

991
01:24:03,203 --> 01:24:05,831
Mbok, change the doctor's bed sheet.

992
01:24:05,915 --> 01:24:08,123
I did it yesterday.

993
01:24:08,207 --> 01:24:13,291
It's still clean anyway. No need to change it.

994
01:24:13,371 --> 01:24:16,246
It's fine. Just change it.
To keep it clean all the time.

995
01:24:22,247 --> 01:24:24,499
Nana is worried that you're not comfortable.

996
01:24:24,579 --> 01:24:28,499
If you don't like it here,
she won't have her own private doctor.

997
01:24:29,359 --> 01:24:30,623
Am I right?

998
01:24:30,707 --> 01:24:32,247
Who is worried? Me or you?

999
01:24:35,791 --> 01:24:39,291
If Titi's not here anymore...

1000
01:24:39,371 --> 01:24:42,454
...it'll be hard for you
to take care of me and Althan. Am I right?

1001
01:24:53,207 --> 01:24:55,407
No. It's okay. Carry on with your breakfast.

1002
01:24:55,491 --> 01:24:58,415
- But Althan's crying.
- He's my son.

1003
01:24:58,499 --> 01:25:02,330
Can't I take care of my own son? I'm her mother.

1004
01:25:04,331 --> 01:25:06,623
- Carry on.
- Sumi is there.

1005
01:25:06,707 --> 01:25:08,791
No. I want to take care of him myself.

1006
01:25:10,955 --> 01:25:12,123
Okay.

1007
01:25:14,955 --> 01:25:16,883
Hey, Malik...

1008
01:25:16,955 --> 01:25:20,123
...from now on,
you don't need to take care of me that much.

1009
01:25:20,207 --> 01:25:23,538
I'm fine. I can do everything myself. I'm healthy.

1010
01:25:26,163 --> 01:25:27,291
Okay?

1011
01:25:27,663 --> 01:25:29,371
Carry on with your breakfast.

1012
01:25:31,003 --> 01:25:32,211
Have a nice breakfast.

1013
01:25:35,831 --> 01:25:40,623
Althan, my son, come here. Why are you crying?

1014
01:25:40,707 --> 01:25:42,707
Come here.

1015
01:25:42,791 --> 01:25:45,307
Honey.

1016
01:25:45,871 --> 01:25:46,915
Ti?

1017
01:25:47,955 --> 01:25:48,999
Hey.

1018
01:25:50,295 --> 01:25:52,055
Why did you ask me to meet you here?

1019
01:25:55,955 --> 01:25:57,331
What's going on?

1020
01:25:57,415 --> 01:25:59,370
I want everything to end, Malik.

1021
01:26:01,623 --> 01:26:04,123
Yes, I also want everything to end.

1022
01:26:04,207 --> 01:26:07,247
I'm tired of pretending.

1023
01:26:07,331 --> 01:26:09,039
Let's talk to Hannah tomorrow.

1024
01:26:10,623 --> 01:26:12,331
That's not what I mean.

1025
01:26:12,415 --> 01:26:13,579
I want...

1026
01:26:15,531 --> 01:26:18,127
...Hannah to remember me as just her best friend.

1027
01:26:19,499 --> 01:26:22,483
So, I'm going to leave your life.

1028
01:26:22,567 --> 01:26:23,662
No.

1029
01:26:25,791 --> 01:26:27,163
No one's leaving.

1030
01:26:27,247 --> 01:26:28,914
Malik, you need to understand.

1031
01:26:32,579 --> 01:26:34,371
I love you.

1032
01:26:35,663 --> 01:26:38,079
But there's someone else
who is more deserving of your love.

1033
01:26:39,163 --> 01:26:41,290
I'm truly happy with you.

1034
01:26:45,499 --> 01:26:48,207
But it's more important for you
to make someone else happy.

1035
01:26:51,707 --> 01:26:53,538
I am your wife.

1036
01:26:56,623 --> 01:26:59,622
But there's someone else
who needs you more as a husband.

1037
01:27:02,163 --> 01:27:03,662
So, you don't need me?

1038
01:27:05,079 --> 01:27:10,830
- You regret this marriage?
- Malik, I will never regret our marriage.

1039
01:27:12,415 --> 01:27:17,455
Marrying you was what I have always wanted.

1040
01:27:18,955 --> 01:27:23,414
And I will remember you forever.

1041
01:27:28,499 --> 01:27:29,830
Forgive me.

1042
01:27:34,039 --> 01:27:36,455
But this is the best thing for all of us.

1043
01:27:37,275 --> 01:27:39,398
You can't just disappear from my life.

1044
01:27:43,455 --> 01:27:46,330
Because now I love two amazing women.

1045
01:28:05,579 --> 01:28:09,039
- Sumi? Mbok? What's going on?
- Ma'am.

1046
01:28:09,123 --> 01:28:12,207
Althan is crying inside.

1047
01:28:12,291 --> 01:28:14,955
But I don't dare to go inside.

1048
01:28:15,039 --> 01:28:18,163
But he's been crying for 30 minutes.
Help me. I'm scared.

1049
01:28:18,247 --> 01:28:21,455
- That's right. The baby can be possessed.
- Right.

1050
01:28:21,539 --> 01:28:24,539
Wait, no. Not possessed.
What are you talking about?

1051
01:28:24,623 --> 01:28:28,246
- Not possessed. Help us.
- Okay, okay.

1052
01:28:33,747 --> 01:28:35,079
Han?

1053
01:28:35,163 --> 01:28:36,455
Who's there?

1054
01:28:36,539 --> 01:28:38,246
It's me, Cathy.

1055
01:28:43,079 --> 01:28:48,039
Can I hold Althan for a while to calm him down?

1056
01:28:50,747 --> 01:28:52,871
Sumi, Mbok...

1057
01:28:52,955 --> 01:28:55,579
- Take care of Althan.
- Yes, Ma'am.

1058
01:28:55,663 --> 01:28:56,830
Be careful, Ma'am.

1059
01:29:02,915 --> 01:29:07,498
Althan needs to familiarize himself with me,
or else there'll be distance between us.

1060
01:29:08,371 --> 01:29:11,331
Han, there's no way that
there'll be distance between the two of you.

1061
01:29:11,415 --> 01:29:13,162
You're his birth mother.

1062
01:29:16,663 --> 01:29:18,954
But in reality, he's closer to you.

1063
01:29:24,499 --> 01:29:25,498
Let's sit.

1064
01:29:32,207 --> 01:29:33,375
Cathy...

1065
01:29:34,000 --> 01:29:35,914
You can take my husband.

1066
01:29:38,455 --> 01:29:39,998
But not my son.

1067
01:29:41,999 --> 01:29:43,746
- Han, what are you...
- Sit.

1068
01:29:44,791 --> 01:29:46,038
Sit down.

1069
01:29:50,831 --> 01:29:52,163
I didn't expect it, you know...

1070
01:29:54,195 --> 01:29:55,850
...for you to be that evil.

1071
01:29:56,579 --> 01:29:57,954
Diabolical.

1072
01:30:00,707 --> 01:30:04,955
- Cath... No.
- Let me explain.

1073
01:30:05,039 --> 01:30:06,291
I saw it myself.

1074
01:30:07,455 --> 01:30:09,539
I saw it clearly.

1075
01:30:11,039 --> 01:30:13,915
You and Malik.

1076
01:30:15,791 --> 01:30:18,079
In your room together.

1077
01:30:18,163 --> 01:30:19,622
Under this roof.

1078
01:30:25,331 --> 01:30:26,999
How could you?

1079
01:30:27,079 --> 01:30:29,331
- You betrayed your own best friend.
- Han...

1080
01:30:31,439 --> 01:30:34,207
- Hannah, please.
- You made my house dirty.

1081
01:30:34,291 --> 01:30:37,163
- Han, please.
- I should've known...

1082
01:30:37,247 --> 01:30:40,206
...that you can never stop loving him.

1083
01:31:01,415 --> 01:31:02,662
Listen to me.

1084
01:31:07,371 --> 01:31:10,498
You can take Malik away. Be my guest.

1085
01:31:13,123 --> 01:31:18,702
Be my guest, Cath.
I don't need a cheater like him.

1086
01:31:24,247 --> 01:31:26,414
But don't take my child away from me.

1087
01:31:33,747 --> 01:31:35,122
In the end...

1088
01:31:36,663 --> 01:31:37,915
...a traitor...

1089
01:31:39,331 --> 01:31:41,330
...will also meet a traitor.

1090
01:32:31,039 --> 01:32:34,039
- Ma'am.
- Ma'am, where are you going?

1091
01:32:35,123 --> 01:32:39,078
Mbok Ipah, Sumi, I'm leaving, okay?

1092
01:32:40,123 --> 01:32:43,499
Please take care of Hannah and Althan.

1093
01:32:43,579 --> 01:32:48,579
Oh, dear. I swear to God,
it wasn't me who told her.

1094
01:32:48,663 --> 01:32:55,946
I used to be Team Mrs. Hannah,
but I've realized that you've done no wrong.

1095
01:32:56,039 --> 01:32:58,499
I know, I believe that.

1096
01:32:58,579 --> 01:33:03,206
Thanks for helping me all this time.

1097
01:33:08,747 --> 01:33:10,038
It's okay.

1098
01:33:28,955 --> 01:33:30,455
Sir!

1099
01:33:30,539 --> 01:33:33,079
The doctor was just leaving,
bringing all of her things.

1100
01:33:33,163 --> 01:33:37,791
- Leaving?
- And Mrs. Hannah asked me to pack her clothes.

1101
01:33:37,871 --> 01:33:40,579
She said she was going to leave, too.

1102
01:33:40,663 --> 01:33:42,247
Oh, dear. Hannah...

1103
01:33:42,331 --> 01:33:44,875
That's why you shouldn't do polygamy.

1104
01:33:44,959 --> 01:33:46,831
- It's not good.
- Bibi!

1105
01:33:46,915 --> 01:33:49,955
- What are you saying?
- That's the reason for all of this!

1106
01:33:50,039 --> 01:33:52,123
- I know!
- What should we do?

1107
01:33:52,207 --> 01:33:54,830
- Poor Mrs. Hannah and the doctor.
- Sir!

1108
01:33:56,415 --> 01:33:59,579
Hannah, hey. What are you doing?

1109
01:33:59,663 --> 01:34:01,163
Leave me alone!

1110
01:34:01,247 --> 01:34:02,415
Hannah, wait.

1111
01:34:02,499 --> 01:34:04,371
Let me go!

1112
01:34:04,455 --> 01:34:06,831
- Hannah, listen to my explanation. Don't cry.
- Let me go!

1113
01:34:06,915 --> 01:34:09,123
I'm not crying because of you.

1114
01:34:10,871 --> 01:34:13,162
You're not worthy of my tears.

1115
01:34:16,183 --> 01:34:21,811
I'm crying because
my thoughts of who you are is all ruined...

1116
01:34:23,775 --> 01:34:26,274
...by the reality of who you actually are.

1117
01:34:28,831 --> 01:34:30,871
- Hey, hold on.
- Malik, let me go!

1118
01:34:30,955 --> 01:34:33,955
I'd like to show you something. Hold on.

1119
01:34:34,039 --> 01:34:35,078
Hold on.

1120
01:34:37,455 --> 01:34:38,538
Look at this.

1121
01:34:40,019 --> 01:34:41,142
Here.

1122
01:34:49,707 --> 01:34:51,746
Why was I there?

1123
01:34:56,291 --> 01:34:58,370
Forgive me for not explaining it to you earlier.

1124
01:35:04,000 --> 01:35:06,454
The marriage happened
because you gave us permission.

1125
01:35:10,831 --> 01:35:12,123
"In the name of Allah."

1126
01:35:13,955 --> 01:35:15,246
In the name of Allah.

1127
01:35:17,499 --> 01:35:19,830
"I will...

1128
01:35:20,831 --> 01:35:23,579
...marry your husband."

1129
01:35:23,663 --> 01:35:28,955
This marriage would never have happened
if Cathy and I didn't want to make you happy.

1130
01:35:29,039 --> 01:35:31,078
And why are you telling me just now?

1131
01:35:40,499 --> 01:35:42,123
Because you have amnesia.

1132
01:35:43,871 --> 01:35:48,330
Cathy didn't want to tell you too soon.
She wanted to wait for you to fully recover.

1133
01:35:53,039 --> 01:35:55,038
You were the one
who asked for this marriage, Hannah.

1134
01:35:56,039 --> 01:35:59,039
You were a witness. You gave us permission.

1135
01:35:59,123 --> 01:36:00,623
But now Cathy yields.

1136
01:36:00,707 --> 01:36:03,454
She doesn't want you
to ever remember this marriage.

1137
01:36:08,163 --> 01:36:10,330
She sacrificed herself for your happiness.

1138
01:36:15,271 --> 01:36:16,979
And now she just wants...

1139
01:36:19,123 --> 01:36:21,830
...me to be with you and Althan.

1140
01:36:26,663 --> 01:36:28,078
We got married for you.

1141
01:36:35,415 --> 01:36:39,038
And now Cathy chooses to part from me for you.

1142
01:37:14,747 --> 01:37:16,163
Forgive me, Cath.

1143
01:37:16,999 --> 01:37:18,330
I'm truly sorry.

1144
01:37:21,779 --> 01:37:23,946
You're an amazing woman, Cath.

1145
01:37:25,915 --> 01:37:29,830
Forgive me for having bad thoughts about you.

1146
01:37:34,179 --> 01:37:38,010
I'm so ungrateful. Forgive me.

1147
01:37:42,487 --> 01:37:45,110
I begged you...

1148
01:37:49,707 --> 01:37:51,498
...to marry Malik.

1149
01:37:53,539 --> 01:37:55,662
And now I'm here...

1150
01:37:57,663 --> 01:37:59,870
...to beg you once more...

1151
01:38:04,079 --> 01:38:05,999
...to come home.

1152
01:38:06,079 --> 01:38:07,454
To our home.

1153
01:38:10,207 --> 01:38:11,746
For your husband.

1154
01:38:15,915 --> 01:38:17,123
For me.

1155
01:38:18,579 --> 01:38:20,331
And our son, Althan.

1156
01:38:22,871 --> 01:38:24,038
Okay?

1157
01:38:52,707 --> 01:38:57,163
<i>No woman wants to be a concubine.</i>

1158
01:38:59,831 --> 01:39:07,162
<i>Every woman dreams of being the first
and the only one loved by the man we love.</i>

1159
01:39:23,831 --> 01:39:27,275
<i>But sometimes destiny tells a different story.</i>

1160
01:39:27,799 --> 01:39:29,999
<i>What's important is how we deal with it.</i>

1161
01:39:30,079 --> 01:39:31,123
How cute.

1162
01:39:31,207 --> 01:39:32,998
One, two...

1163
01:39:37,079 --> 01:39:42,623
<i>Because happiness is not what we fantasize about.</i>

1164
01:39:42,707 --> 01:39:44,871
<i>But what we're living.</i>

1165
01:39:44,955 --> 01:39:46,290
Clap your hands.

1166
01:39:48,991 --> 01:39:49,991
Ti.

1167
01:39:51,331 --> 01:39:52,415
Tell her.

1168
01:39:54,079 --> 01:39:57,663
Later. Or you tell her.

1169
01:39:57,747 --> 01:40:00,371
- You should tell her.
- Tell me what?

1170
01:40:02,615 --> 01:40:03,822
Cath?

1171
01:40:07,163 --> 01:40:08,326
What?

1172
01:40:15,095 --> 01:40:16,294
Cathy pregnant.

1173
01:40:21,887 --> 01:40:23,218
Seriously?

1174
01:40:25,455 --> 01:40:27,290
You're pregnant, Cath?

1175
01:40:28,791 --> 01:40:31,414
Thank God.

1176
01:40:33,579 --> 01:40:35,870
This is truly a miracle.

1177
01:40:37,147 --> 01:40:39,606
Althan will soon have a sibling.

1178
01:40:41,871 --> 01:40:44,038
Although it's not from my womb.

1179
01:40:48,163 --> 01:40:50,623
Congrats.

1180
01:40:50,707 --> 01:40:52,122
Thank you.

1181
01:40:57,323 --> 01:40:59,242
Althan will soon have a sibling.

1182
01:41:08,455 --> 01:41:13,414
<i>And with Malik and Hannah,
I can feel the happiness of sharing.</i>

1183
01:41:18,207 --> 01:41:24,415
<i>We fill each other's lives, we learn from each other,
we give to one another, and we love each other.</i>

1184
01:41:24,499 --> 01:41:28,206
<i>And we can be happy in our own way.</i>

1185
01:41:36,331 --> 01:41:40,831
Good morning, my loves.

1186
01:41:40,915 --> 01:41:42,870
I'm happy to see you.

1187
01:41:44,163 --> 01:41:45,371
So beautiful.

1188
01:41:47,455 --> 01:41:52,707
I bet you're happy to see me happy
with my husband.

1189
01:41:52,791 --> 01:41:55,539
With my son.

1190
01:41:55,623 --> 01:41:57,414
With my husband's concubine.

1191
01:42:10,455 --> 01:42:11,579
Hannah?

1192
01:42:11,663 --> 01:42:12,791
Oh, dear.

1193
01:42:13,947 --> 01:42:15,486
Hannah? Oh, dear!

1194
01:42:17,851 --> 01:42:19,782
Oh, dear! Ma'am!

1195
01:42:21,803 --> 01:42:24,007
- Hannah?
- Malik.

1196
01:42:24,923 --> 01:42:26,630
She's still unconscious.

1197
01:42:28,539 --> 01:42:29,707
But how is she doing?

1198
01:42:29,791 --> 01:42:33,831
The doctors have checked her and...

1199
01:42:33,915 --> 01:42:35,290
Let's hope she wakes up soon.

1200
01:42:37,455 --> 01:42:38,871
Malik.

1201
01:42:38,955 --> 01:42:40,079
Hannah?

1202
01:42:43,415 --> 01:42:44,454
Hannah?

1203
01:42:49,247 --> 01:42:50,414
Cath?

1204
01:42:56,131 --> 01:43:01,922
I'm thankful that God has given me time...

1205
01:43:04,747 --> 01:43:06,746
...to meet Althan.

1206
01:43:08,371 --> 01:43:10,662
To play with him.

1207
01:43:13,087 --> 01:43:14,834
And I'm certain...

1208
01:43:17,999 --> 01:43:19,290
...my husband...

1209
01:43:20,535 --> 01:43:22,119
...and my son...

1210
01:43:23,895 --> 01:43:26,478
...will be happy with you.

1211
01:43:28,915 --> 01:43:31,830
I'm ready for God to call me to His side.

1212
01:43:33,955 --> 01:43:35,831
Han...

1213
01:43:35,915 --> 01:43:37,871
Don't say that.

1214
01:43:38,791 --> 01:43:40,331
You have to remember...

1215
01:43:43,371 --> 01:43:46,538
...I will always be with you two.

1216
01:43:50,791 --> 01:43:53,290
I will always love you two.

1217
01:44:03,415 --> 01:44:04,830
And we...

1218
01:44:08,747 --> 01:44:12,330
We will always be together.

1219
01:45:03,507 --> 01:45:04,507
Hannah.

1220
01:45:05,655 --> 01:45:08,419
Although we live together
only for a short time...

1221
01:45:09,903 --> 01:45:12,967
...but you give me a lot of lessons.

1222
01:45:14,171 --> 01:45:15,802
About love...

1223
01:45:16,467 --> 01:45:18,003
...sincerity...

1224
01:45:18,903 --> 01:45:20,631
...and sacrifice.

1225
01:45:21,755 --> 01:45:25,051
And I will tell our son...

1226
01:45:26,091 --> 01:45:30,286
...that he's lucky
to have had an amazing mother.

1227
01:45:35,107 --> 01:45:36,107
Han...

1228
01:45:37,607 --> 01:45:40,655
...I'm a nobody compared to you.

1229
01:45:42,843 --> 01:45:44,983
And until the end of time...

1230
01:45:46,255 --> 01:45:48,951
...I can never replace you.

1231
01:45:50,207 --> 01:45:54,802
But I will try to fulfill your wish...

1232
01:45:56,411 --> 01:45:58,263
...to care for...

1233
01:45:58,515 --> 01:46:01,191
...and to love Malik and Althan...

1234
01:46:01,679 --> 01:46:04,355
...as much as you love...

1235
01:46:04,855 --> 01:46:06,582
...and care for them.
